ASoC: dapm: Use snd_soc_dapm_add_path() in snd_soc_dapm_new_pcm()

We already know the widgets we want to connect, so use snd_soc_dapm_add_path()
instead of snd_soc_dapm_add_route() in snd_soc_dapm_new_pcm().

